Avoid Common Loan Application Mistakes
Many business owners delay approval by making avoidable errors.
Common mistakes include:
    • Incomplete applications 
    • Unrealistic revenue projections 
    • Poor bookkeeping 
    • Applying for excessive funding 
    • Missing required documents 
    • Ignoring credit issues 
    • Providing inconsistent financial information 
Carefully reviewing your application before submission can improve approval odds and reduce processing delays.
